,"tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-praise-hamd","tag-providence-al-qada-wal-qadr","tag-self-al-nafs","tag-supplication-al-dua"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-5Va","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":17455,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/02\/qadr-reward-sabr-shukr\/","url_meta":{"origin":22764,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Shukr: Believer is rewarded for patience or gratitude","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 2, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI am amazed by the believer. If he is granted goodness, he praises Allah and is grateful. If he is afflicted with a calamity, he praises Allah and is patient. The believer is rewarded\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34306,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/19\/praises-allah-during-hardship\/","url_meta":{"origin":22764,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hamd: Reward of praising Allah during hardship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 19, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Shaddad ibn Aws reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty says: When I put one of my faithful servants to trial and he praises Me despite his trial, he will rise from his bed free of sin like the day he was\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hik